# VROL-491 — Rust engine build artefacts. The `pkg/` dir is generated
# by `pnpm run build:engine-rs`; tracking it would churn the repo on
# every rebuild. CI (VROL-509 output-parity spike onwards) will run
# the wasm-pack build fresh.
engine-rs/target/
engine-rs/pkg/
engine-rs/Cargo.lock
